" aria-label="Share on facebook"><span class="bk gk gl gm"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M19.75 12.04c0-4.3-3.47-7.79-7.75-7.79a7.77 7.77 0 0 0-5.9 12.84 7.77 7.77 0 0 0 4.69 2.63v-5.49h-1.9v-2.2h1.9v-1.62c0-1.88 1.14-2.9 2.8-2.9.8 0 1.49.06 1.69.08v1.97h-1.15c-.91 0-1.1.43-1.1 1.07v1.4h2.17l-.28 2.2h-1.88v5.52a7.77 7.77 0 0 0 6.7-7.71" fill="#A8A8A8"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><div class="gp l dw"><div><div class="bk" aria-hidden="false"><button class="ae af ag ah ai aj ak al am an ao ap aq ar as" aria-label="Share on linkedin"><span class="bk gk gl gm"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M19.75 5.39v13.22a1.14 1.14 0 0 1-1.14 1.14H5.39a1.14 1.14 0 0 1-1.14-1.14V5.39a1.14 1.14 0 0 1 1.14-1.14h13.22a1.14 1.14 0 0 1 1.14 1.14zM8.81 10.18H6.53v7.3H8.8v-7.3zM9 7.67a1.31 1.31 0 0 0-1.3-1.32h-.04a1.32 1.32 0 0 0 0 2.64A1.31 1.31 0 0 0 9 7.71v-.04zm8.46 5.37c0-2.2-1.4-3.05-2.78-3.05a2.6 2.6 0 0 0-2.3 1.18h-.07v-1h-2.14v7.3h2.28V13.6a1.51 1.51 0 0 1 1.36-1.63h.09c.72 0 1.26.45 1.26 1.6v3.91h2.28l.02-4.43z" fill="#A8A8A8"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><div class="l dw"><div><div class="bk" aria-hidden="false"><button class="ae af ag ah ai aj ak al am an ao ap aq ar as"><span class="bk gk gl gm"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M3.57 14.67c0-.57.13-1.11.38-1.6l.02-.02v-.02l.02-.02c0-.02 0-.02.02-.02.12-.26.3-.52.57-.8L7.78 9v-.02l.01-.02c.44-.41.91-.7 1.44-.85a4.87 4.87 0 0 0-1.19 2.36A5.04 5.04 0 0 0 8 11.6L6.04 13.6c-.19.19-.32.4-.38.65a2 2 0 0 0 0 .9c.08.2.2.4.38.57l1.29 1.31c.27.28.62.42 1.03.42.42 0 .78-.14 1.06-.42l1.23-1.25.79-.78 1.15-1.16c.08-.09.19-.22.28-.4.1-.2.15-.42.15-.67 0-.16-.02-.3-.06-.45l-.02-.02v-.02l-.07-.14s0-.03-.04-.06l-.06-.13-.02-.02c0-.02 0-.03-.02-.05a.6.6 0 0 0-.14-.16l-.48-.5c0-.04.02-.1.04-.15l.06-.12 1.17-1.14.09-.09.56.57c.02.04.08.1.16.18l.05.04.03.06.04.05.03.04.04.06.1.14.02.02c0 .02.01.03.03.04l.1.2v.02c.1.16.2.38.3.68a1 1 0 0 1 .04.25 3.2 3.2 0 0 1 .02 1.33 3.49 3.49 0 0 1-.95 1.87l-.66.67-.97.97-1.56 1.57a3.4 3.4 0 0 1-2.47 1.02c-.97 0-1.8-.34-2.49-1.03l-1.3-1.3a3.55 3.55 0 0 1-1-2.51v-.01h-.02v.02zm5.39-3.43c0-.19.02-.4.07-.63.13-.74.44-1.37.95-1.87l.66-.67.97-.98 1.56-1.56c.68-.69 1.5-1.03 2.47-1.03.97 0 1.8.34 2.48 1.02l1.3 1.32a3.48 3.48 0 0 1 1 2.48c0 .58-.11 1.11-.37 1.6l-.02.02v.02l-.02.04c-.14.27-.35.54-.6.8L16.23 15l-.01.02-.01.02c-.44.42-.92.7-1.43.83a4.55 4.55 0 0 0 1.23-3.52L18 10.38c.18-.21.3-.42.35-.65a2.03 2.03 0 0 0-.01-.9 1.96 1.96 0 0 0-.36-.58l-1.3-1.3a1.49 1.49 0 0 0-1.06-.42c-.42 0-.77.14-1.06.4l-1.2 1.27-.8.8-1.16 1.15c-.08.08-.18.21-.29.4a1.66 1.66 0 0 0-.08 1.12l.02.03v.02l.06.14s.01.03.05.06l.06.13.02.02.01.02.01.02c.05.08.1.13.14.16l.47.5c0 .04-.02.09-.04.15l-.06.12-1.15 1.15-.1.08-.56-.56a2.3 2.3 0 0 0-.18-.19c-.02-.01-.02-.03-.02-.04l-.02-.02a.37.37 0 0 1-.1-.12c-.03-.03-.05-.04-.05-.06l-.1-.15-.02-.02-.02-.04-.08-.17v-.02a5.1 5.1 0 0 1-.28-.69 1.03 1.03 0 0 1-.04-.26c-.06-.23-.1-.46-.1-.7v.01z" fill="#A8A8A8"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><div class="bl l"><div><div class="bk" aria-hidden="false"></div></div></div></div></header><span class="l"></span><section><div><div class="ds gv gw gx gy gz"></div><div class="ha hb hc hd he"><div class=""><h1 id="060a" class="pw-post-title hf hg hh bd hi hj hk hl hm hn ho hp hq hr hs ht hu hv hw hx hy hz ia ib ic id bi">EVE Online Enters Web3</h1></div><p id="7056" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><strong class="ig hi"><em class="jc">CCP Games</em></strong><em class="jc"> new venture &amp; what that means for </em><strong class="ig hi"><em class="jc">Star Atlas</em></strong></p><p id="702b" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><a class="ae jd" href="https://www.ccpgames.com/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><strong class="ig hi">CCP Games</strong></a>, creator of the famous massive multiplayer <a class="ae jd" href="https://www.eveonline.com/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><strong class="ig hi">EVE Online</strong></a>, recently announced that it’s secured <strong class="ig hi">$40 million in financing</strong> from external partners to build a new AAA title utilizing blockchain technology, set within the EVE Universe. This news immediately sent ripples through the blockchain community, especially<strong class="ig hi"> </strong><a class="ae jd" href="https://play.staratlas.com/?oid=3&amp;affid=253" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><strong class="ig hi">Star Atlas</strong></a> (currently being built on Solana), as it represents a significant competitor in the development of space-based web3 games.</p><p id="6bb3" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">CCP Games is currently at the forefront of developing a fun-to-play space-themed game, prioritizing player-driven social systems, in-game economies, and self-organizing corporations. As such, the announcement of its own AAA title has significant implications. One question many have asked is how this announcement might effect web3 startups such as Star Atlas, which are being built from the ground up. <em class="jc">How might Star Atlas look to compete</em> against CCP Games’ $40 million traditional financing?</p><figure class="jf jg jh ji fd jj er es paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jk jl di jm bf jn"><div class="er es je"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*vA6RvdtcTBx39i6i1wXDAQ.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="https://www.eveonline.com/" class="bf jo jp c" width="700" height="260" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div><figcaption class="jq jr et er es js jt bd b be z dx"><a class="ae jd" href="https://www.eveonline.com/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Eve Online</a></figcaption></figure><h2 id="e609" class="ju jv hh bd jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke ip kf kg kh it ki kj kk ix kl km kn ko bi">EVE Online and Web3 Gaming Principles</h2><p id="16ae" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih kp ij ik il kq in io ip kr ir is it ks iv iw ix kt iz ja jb ha bi">Backing up, EVE Online is a sci-fi MMO which has been in development since 2003. It’s set in a vast, open universe that allows players to create their own stories and shape their own path through trading, mining, fighting, and exploration. The game’s economy is entirely player-driven, and players can form their own corporations to compete with others for resources and territory.</p><p id="5930" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">These principles align closely with the principles of web3 gaming, which aim to create a fun and open gaming experience that prioritizes player agency and “implied ownership”. In some ways, you might say that traditional gaming companies could have an advantage here. They’ve already given out what players want most: The experience. Enabling true player ownership of in-game assets and the creation of decentralized economies has been something they’ve been unable or unwilling to do until now. One great challenge Web3 has going forward is to create a protective barrier between real economy and <strong class="ig hi">pay-to-win</strong>. After all, pay-to-win is why traditional gamers look at Web3 in such poor taste.</p><figure class="jf jg jh ji fd jj er es paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jk jl di jm bf jn"><div class="er es ku"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*uZ42oi5lBKF8dVE6xweqiQ.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="" class="bf jo jp c" width="700" height="354" loading="lazy" role="presentation"/></picture></div></div></figure><p id="0a17" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">But Web3 startup companies like <strong class="ig hi">Star Atlas aim to change all of that</strong>. They’ve built their core economic principles from the ground up, without the preconceived, centralized mentality that CCP Games will be coming from. It’s still hard to know for sure, but the likelihood of Star Atlas being much more decentralized and equipped to take on Web3’s new frontier seems incredibly promising. Money doesn’t often change a company’s values and principles overnight.</p><h2 id="64cf" class="ju jv hh bd jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke ip kf kg kh it ki kj kk ix kl km kn ko bi">Collaboration Between Big Players</h2><p id="9d25" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih kp ij ik il kq in io ip kr ir is it ks iv iw ix kt iz ja jb ha bi">Something that also needs to be said in 2023 is that for those projects that do find success in the Web3 space, there’s much more room for collaboration than there had been previously. Instead of two companies feeling the need to compete exclusively against one another, collaborations are much more likely to explode as developers find common grounds in <strong class="ig hi">smart contract ecosystems</strong> built from code. Therefore, the release of “<a class="ae jd" href="https://www.projectawakening.io/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><strong class="ig hi">Project Awakening</strong></a>” (which is what CCP Games is currently calling the project) should be exciting news to Web3 as well as the Star Atlas community.<strong class="ig hi"> Open source blockchain tools</strong> being developed by “Project Awakening” may have massive benefits for Star Atlas and vice versa.</p><p id="9387" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">CCP Games’ DAOs could likely become unmatched in Web3 space-faring games. Experience with EVE Online gives it a unique perspective in the development of an immersive game. The company has spent years developing player-driven social systems, open economies, and self-organizing corporations, very similar to what DAOs strive to become. As such, it’s well-positioned to build a project that embodies these principles.</p><figure class="jf jg jh ji fd jj er es paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jk jl di jm bf jn"><div class="er es kv"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*tSOXDXBYBm2FIBZcjdR8MQ.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="" class="bf jo jp c" width="700" height="372" loading="lazy" role="presentation"/></picture></div></div></figure><h2 id="2162" class="ju jv hh bd jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke ip kf kg kh it ki kj kk ix kl km kn ko bi">CCP Games Leadership and Finances</h2><p id="fdfc" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih kp ij ik il kq in io ip kr ir is it ks iv iw ix kt iz ja jb ha bi">CCP Games CEO Hilmar Pétursson has been a vocal proponent of blockchain technology since around 2017. He’s spent these last several years advocating for blockchain’s potential to enable “true player ownership” and “open and secure economies.” Pétursson’s experience with web3 gaming and blockchain technology makes him an ideal partner for <a class="ae jd" href="https://a16z.com/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><strong class="ig hi">a16z</strong></a>, the leading venture capital firm that’s invested heavily into “Project Awakening”.</p><p id="7e02" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">The collaboration between CCP Games and a16z will also help to accelerate the development of the infant web3 community. It has the potential to establish new standards for the development of web3 gaming principles and open economies.</p><blockquote class="kw kx ky"><p id="22c9" class="ie if jc ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io kz iq ir is la iu iv iw lb iy iz ja jb ha bi">“Together, we share the belief that player ownership and governance within an open platform can be a key source of fun that serves to amplify great gameplay and captivating game design.” (<a class="ae jd" href="https://a16z.com/2023/03/21/investing-in-ccp-games/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">a16z.com</a>)</p></blockquote><figure class="jf jg jh ji fd jj er es paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jk jl di jm bf jn"><div class="er es lc"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/0*Z05NoUkwQH2tFBmx.jpg 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="" class="bf jo jp c" width="700" height="195" loading="lazy" role="presentation"/></picture></div></div><figcaption class="jq jr et er es js jt bd b be z dx"><a class="ae jd" href="https://mmos.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/eve-online-quantum-cores-update-banner.jpg" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Eve Online Quantum Cores</a></figcaption></figure><h2 id="e983" class="ju jv hh bd jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke ip kf kg kh it ki kj kk ix kl km kn ko bi">The Impact on Star Atlas</h2><p id="e5a8" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih kp ij ik il kq in io ip kr ir is it ks iv iw ix kt iz ja jb ha bi">While CCP Games’ $40 million is undoubtedly a significant investment in this project, it could also have unintended consequences for ground-up web3 ventures like Star Atlas. It could be a benefit by creating a more supportive ecosystem for its own development, but it could also draw players away. Will Project Awakening players start from scratch or will its userbase be able to transfer their current EVE Online accounts to the new title? That would be quite the onboarding achievement as they’re currently sitting at <strong class="ig hi">9.6 million</strong> existing <strong class="ig hi">accounts</strong> as well as approximately <strong class="ig hi">170,000 active players</strong>.</p><figure class="jf jg jh ji fd jj er es paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jk jl di jm bf jn"><div class="er es ld"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*z2KH8u9EVxJZDA6lDn5sPg.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="" class="bf jo jp c" width="700" height="319" loading="lazy" role="presentation"/></picture></div></div></figure><p id="e604" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">We want to see Star Atlas succeed and believe that <strong class="ig hi">competition is healthy</strong> for the growth of any sprouting industry. As CCP develops this new AAA title, we will of course be comparing it closely to the current Web3 giant Star Atlas. While the partnership with a16z gives explosive potential to CCP Games’ efforts to create a groundbreaking title, we hope to see them embrace the freeing principles that Star Atlas currently embraces, rather than grasping onto the constraining technologies and greedy mentalities of the past.</p><p id="7bc7" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">It will be fascinating to see how this project evolves. As space-exploration lovers ourselves, we at <a class="le lf ge" href="https://medium.com/u/ed24b40c4906?source=post_page-----9a7913c194d3--------------------------------" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Hologram News Network</a> promise to keep you updated with the most significant Star Atlas News available and will also keep you posted as this new project unfolds. Make sure to <strong class="ig hi">follow us on social media</strong> for more.</p><h2 id="41b8" class="ju jv hh bd jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke ip kf kg kh it ki kj kk ix kl km kn ko bi">About the Author</h2><p id="3c9f" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih kp ij ik il kq in io ip kr ir is it ks iv iw ix kt iz ja jb ha bi"><a class="ae jd" rel="noopener" href="/@punaab"><strong class="ig hi">Oni Merchant</strong></a><strong class="ig hi"> </strong>is a writer on <a class="ae jd" href="https://medium.com/the-hologram" rel="noopener">The Hologram News Network</a>, an independent blockchain gaming meta-news organization devoted to the coverage of Star Atlas. Follow him on Twitter @<a class="ae jd" href="https://twitter.com/OniMerchant" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">OniMerchant</a>.</p><p id="8fcf" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">Follow The Hologram on Social Media:</p><p id="9b8e" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><a class="ae jd" href="https://open.spotify.com/show/2mxndrDW6yPfpS350ijzjt?si=ec7c717f998240d6" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Podcast</a> | <a class="ae jd" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDa-YxgNG6A9xpH1qyP0OaQ" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">YouTube</a> | <a class="ae jd" href="https://twitter.com/home" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Twitter</a> | <a class="ae jd" href="https://twitter.com/home" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Instagram</a> | <a class="ae jd" href="https://thehologram.io/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Web</a></p><h2 id="0ad4" class="ju jv hh bd jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke ip kf kg kh it ki kj kk ix kl km kn ko bi">About The Hologram</h2><p id="edbc" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih kp ij ik il kq in io ip kr ir is it ks iv iw ix kt iz ja jb ha bi"><a class="ae jd" href="https://medium.com/the-hologram" rel="noopener">The Hologram</a> is Star Atlas’ first and only independent news network. Our vision is to become the most trusted source of information about Star Atlas and a voice for the whole community. Readers can expect a high standard from our reporting and staff. Our promise to you: we will not publish anything that hasn’t been thoroughly researched and based on the best facts available.</p><figure class="jf jg jh ji fd jj er es paragraph-image"><div class="er es lg"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1260/format:webp/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 1260w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 630px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/0*kNUnYUrZnWMQ3gQ1.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:82